Boy Facing Girl In Toddler Wrestling Match Makes A Hilarious Move   
A young boy took a different tactic when facing off against a little girl in his first ever wrestling match. The short clip opens with the pair getting ready in the wrestling ring. They shake hands, get into their poses and then…where is he going? The little boy hilariously opts to run around in circles instead of facing his opponent! I love how the little girl shrugs as she chases after him! 
The funny clip is going viral because it’s absolutely adorable! 
Click on the play button to start the video.
